author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Magellan Health Q4 Earnings Per Share $2.17
text:
Feb 27 (Reuters) - Magellan Health Inc:
* MAGELLAN HEALTH REPORTS FOURTH QUARTER 2017 AND FULL YEAR FINANCIAL RESULTS
* QTRLY ‍ADJ EARNINGS PER SHARE $ 2.55​ * QTRLY EARNINGS PER SHARE $2.17 * QTRLY ‍NET REVENUE $1,694.4 MILLION VERSUS $1,263.4 MILLION​
* FOR 2018, CO NOW EXPECTS FULLY DILUTED EPS TO BE BETWEEN $4.88 AND $5.82
* FOR 2018, SEES FULLY DILUTED ADJUSTED EPS TO BE BETWEEN $6.37 AND $7.15
* FOR 2018, CO IS MAINTAINING ITS REVENUE RANGE AT $7.5 BILLION TO $7.8 BILLION
* Q4 EARNINGS PER SHARE VIEW $2.29, REVENUE VIEW $1.62 BILLION -- THOMSON REUTERS I/B/E/S Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
